接口 IBeaconDataFactory

  • 所有已知实现类:
    NullIBeaconDataFactory

    public interface IBeaconDataFactory
    This can be configured for the public iBeacon data store, or a private iBeacon data store. In the public data store, you can read any value but only write to the values to the ibeacons you created
